text: Willy Möhwald (1 September 1908 - 15 May 1975) was a Czech ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1928 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1908 births Category:1975 deaths Category:Czech male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Czechoslovakia Category:Ski jumpers at the 1928 Winter Olympics
